snippet.textDisplay:
Just think, for these lines… we remember some Devi(ma,behan,nani,biwi) when they left us and only the body in front of us…and while they are alive they asked us “how am I looking with this Kala bindi…beautiful right ? “ 

“Har Koi Kaajal Laau Ree
Mohey Kaala Tika Lagaao Ree
Unki Chhab Se Dikhu Main To Pyaari
Lachhmi Ji Vaaro
Nazar Utaaro
Aaj Mere Piya Ghar Aavenge” 🥺
